description: This file declares the exported API functions for the Slap Obj Agent Object in the Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP) component. It includes function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling objects, initializing, and resetting the object, serving as an interface for external modules.

methods.name: SlapCreateObjAgent
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Slap Obj Agent object.

methods.name: SlapOaoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the OAO object.

methods.name: SlapOaoRemove
methods.description: Removes an instance of the OAO object.

methods.name: SlapOaoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls the necessary objects for the OAO.

methods.name: SlapOaoReset
methods.description: Resets the state of the OAO object.
